<subSubSection id="C34C655AFFB353432061F59057D1B10D" pageId="2" pageNumber="433" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="8BE936D1FFB353432061F59057D1B10D" blockId="2.[1372,2578,2222,2764]" pageId="2" pageNumber="433">
<emphasis id="B922EAC3FFB353432061F5905985B125" bold="true" box="[1375,1723,2615,2644]" pageId="2" pageNumber="433">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Shiny Guinea Pig has a wide distribution and occurs in protected areas.
</paragraph>
